<h1>Booklist</h1>
This is a list of books. The list is paginated and ordered descending by date listed. </p>

Anyone can comment on a book!</p>

<% unless current_admin %>

But you will have to sign up if you want to be an Admin so you can add and edit books and delete them as well! </p>

